Description: The Champion Power Equipment 100384 3200 psi 2.4-GPM Dolly-Style Gas Pressure Washer provides cost-effective, "do-it-yourself" cleaning power. Item Name: 320 Psi 20-Volt Hydroshot Power Nozzle
Description: The Worx Hydroshot (WG629) is the first-of-its-kind, truly portable, self-pressurized power cleaning and watering device. Its compact and efficient engineering makes it ideal for quick and easy cleaning tasks and eliminates the need for bulky hoses and clunky pressure washers that can damage your items and surfaces. Two-speed operation allows for additional power when your project demands it or increased runtime depending on your preference. The Worx Hydroshot (WG629) is a member of the Worx 20-Volt Power Share platform so the battery is compatible with the entire line of Worx 20-Volt DIY yard and power tools.

Item Name: 9.4GA13 4,000 psi 3.3 GPM AAA Triplex Plunger Horizontal Pump with Brass Head and Powerboost Technology
Description: The AAA 9.4GA13 is a direct drive horizontal triplex plunger pump rated at 4,000 psi max pressure at 3.3 GPM max water flow. The AAA 9.4GA13 has a forged brass manifold for strength and durability. It is designed with a gas engine flange and 1 in. hollow shaft that fits most horizontal shaft engines. All AAA pumps come pre-filled with oil and are equipped with thermal relief protection to prevent pump overheating. Designed with a 3/8 in. quick connect pump outlet for easy connection to the pressure hose and an easy start feature to make start up a breeze. The crankcase is manufactured from fully anodized die cast aluminum for corrosion protection and is sealed to prevent contamination and lube failure. High performance double seal system prevents water leaks. Dual oversized radial ball bearings are installed for better wear and friction resistance and precision polished ceramic pistons for extended seal life. It also comes equipped with patent pending PowerBoost Technology to enhance cleaning performance, reduce vibration and heat transfer to deliver a better working environment for the operator while extending engine and pump life. All AAA pump kits come complete with detergent injection siphon tube with filter for chemical cleaning, new mounting bolts and 1/4 in. shaft key.

Description: You name it, you aim it, grime is gone. Make your cleaning chores more mobile with the perfectly portable GO ANYWHERE Pressure Washer from Sun Joe. And the onboard five Quick Connect tips allow you to tailor your spray to suit any cleaning task. Quickly swap interchangeable nozzles to go from a high-pressure 0 pencil point jet to a 40 fan spray, or simply use the soap nozzle to give your cleaning spray a sudsy boost. Fight back against dirt with the SPX3200 and Go With Joe.
